{
  "texts": [
    "The functionality category exhibits the highest degree of implementation, with 5 out of 7 features being effectively executed by all the tools.",
    "The remaining two features, namely authentication and project auditing, are implemented by 18 and 9 tools, respectively.",
    "The other categories present a more heterogeneous scenario.",
    "Within the retrieval category, only reference importing is implemented by all tools.",
    "Interestingly, no tools provide the ability to automatically retrieve the reference of a paper from bibliographic databases."
  ]
}